{"data":[{"date":"21:43 13/08","title":"Bayern Munich nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c vui t\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/bayern-munich-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-tu-tru-cot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb ph\u00eda HLV Niko Kovac.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Alaba d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Eintracht Frankfurt trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao, \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Niko Kovac l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Niko Kovac l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/David-Alaba-chan-thuong,-HLV-Niko-Kovac-len-tieng-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alaba d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0Eintracht Frankfurt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Robert Lewandowski \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0 Eintracht Frankfurt gi\u00fap \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eaft.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Eintracht Frankfurt, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c1o g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau pha va ch\u1ea1m m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Bayern n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Alaba</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c1o, HLV Niko Kovac \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb ph\u00eda t\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alba\" title=\"Alba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/bayern-munich-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-tu-tru-cot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alaba kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Alaba g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Eintracht Frankfurt, \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Alaba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u bao nhi\u00eau l\u00e2u, Alaba v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern Munich s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 danh hi\u1ec7u Bundesliga v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 24 th\u00e1ng 8, \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Bundesliga 2018/19 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Hoffenheim.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2333","checkdouble":"194414"},{"date":"22:01 13/08","title":"Kante n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/kante-noi-gi-ve-vi-tri-moi-duoi-thoi-hlv-sarri.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>NGolo Kante ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Maurizio Sarri.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kante v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 NGolo Kante th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u00f4ng minh lu\u00f4n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 trong vai tr\u00f2 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"NGolo Kante ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"NGolo Kante ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/NGolo-Kante-phat-bieu-ve-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri, vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a anh trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, Kante \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i cao h\u01a1n v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 cho Jorginho.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Kante ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho The Blues sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea5t hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Kante ch\u1ec9 ghi 1 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kante n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">NGolo Kante ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Maurizio Sarri.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante mo ty so cho Chelsea\" title=\"Kante m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Diem-nhan-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-vong-1-Ngoai-hang-Anh-201819-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi, trong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Chelsea s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u1ed1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Arsenal, \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cArsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e2n binh. Mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2332","checkdouble":"194415"},{"date":"22:56 13/08","title":"Alan Shearer: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Pogba t\u1edbi Barca\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/alan-shearer-toi-se-khong-ngac-nhien-neu-pogba-toi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018, s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nat Phillips cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Anfield.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Klavan cho Newcastle</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Ragnar Klavan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Liverpool-ban-Ragnar-Klavan-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Klavan cho Newcastle</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Newcastle \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 6 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986, song HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Matip v\u00e0 Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ragnar Klavan ra \u0111i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ragnar Klavan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Van Dijk v\u00e0 Gomez \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, vi\u1ec7c Matip v\u00e0 Lovren s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u00e0i d\u00e0i. Klavan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Klavan</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018, s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nat Phillips cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Anfield.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klavan vs Aguero\" title=\"Klavan vs Aguero\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/3/19/Thong-tin-luc-luong-tran-Brighton-vs-Liverpool-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klavan s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, sao tr\u1ebb Nat Phillips \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, HLV Klopp s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Klavan ra \u0111i, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Italia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i, Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Klavan th\u00ec Divock Origi v\u00e0 Sheyi Ojo c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Anfield, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2331","checkdouble":"194416"},{"date":"22:56 13/08","title":"\"Bom x\u1ecbt\" Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AC Milan trong v\u00e0i gi\u1edd t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/bom-xit-chelsea-ky-hop-dong-voi-ac-milan-trong-vai-gio-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo Goal c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u01a1i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Italia \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Bakayoko</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTiemoue Bakayoko \u0111ang g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf Chelsea, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Sarri s\u1edf h\u1eefu Kante, Jorginho, Fabregas, Barkley, Drinkwater v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u00e2n binh Kovacic n\u1eefa, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Bakayoko \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Tiemoue-Bakayoko-toi-AC-Milan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tiemoue Bakayoko \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c AC Milan quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Chelsea, AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ef1u sao Monaco.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/them-mot-cau-thu-sap-roi-chelsea-172-194238.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan</span> \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo Goal c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u01a1i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Italia \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, AC Milan s\u1ebd m\u01b0\u1ee3n Bakayoko m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 5 tri\u1ec7u euro, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 35 tri\u1ec7u euro. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 AC Milan b\u1ecf ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 40 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bakayoko s\u1eafp ra m\u1eaft AC Milan</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo Goal c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u01a1i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Italia \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/9/Tiemoue-Bakayoko-toi-AC-Milan-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bakayoko s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AC Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBakayoko \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi Milan v\u00e0o h\u00f4m qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Milan. Anh \u0111ang di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong v\u00e0i gi\u1edd t\u1edbi. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Chelsea nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf s\u00e2n San Siro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho AC Milan, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 b\u1edfi trong tay HLV Sarri \u0111ang c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2330","checkdouble":"194417"},{"date":"23:25 13/08","title":"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \"th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng\" c\u1ee7a Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/3-doi-bong-anh-muon-co-than-dong-cua-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh bao g\u1ed3m Middlebrough, Aston Villa v\u00e0 Derby County mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Martin Odegaard r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martin Odegaard kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMartin Odegaard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u201cth\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng\u201d c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Na Uy, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Odegaard bat ngo duoc dang ky da Champions League\" title=\"Odegaard b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd \u0111\u00e1 Champions League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/9/4/Nghi-van-Zidane-lai-bi-ep-dung-Odegaard-o-Champions-League-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Odegaard kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Na Uy gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid t\u1eeb Stromsgodset v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1/2015. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu Odegaard l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nOdegaard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi CLB Heerenveen c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. Trong th\u1eddi gian cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Heerenveen, sao tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i ra s\u00e2n t\u1edbi 38 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap anh tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u1edf Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Odegaard, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Odegaard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh bao g\u1ed3m Middlebrough, Aston Villa v\u00e0 Derby County mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Martin Odegaard r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Martin Odegaard r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Martin Odegaard r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/3-doi-bong-anh-muon-co-than-dong-cua-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Odegaard s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng CLB \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n, qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Na Uy c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Anh ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng hay kh\u00f4ng. Hi\u1ec7n Odegaard \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 anh t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2329","checkdouble":"194418"},{"date":"23:40 13/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/24/day-cai-ten-tiep-theo-roi-liverpool-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018, s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nat Phillips cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Anfield.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Klavan cho Newcastle</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Ragnar Klavan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Liverpool-ban-Ragnar-Klavan-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Klavan cho Newcastle</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Newcastle \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 6 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986, song HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Matip v\u00e0 Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ragnar Klavan ra \u0111i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ragnar Klavan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Van Dijk v\u00e0 Gomez \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, vi\u1ec7c Matip v\u00e0 Lovren s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u00e0i d\u00e0i. Klavan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Klavan</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018, s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nat Phillips cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Anfield.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klavan vs Aguero\" title=\"Klavan vs Aguero\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/3/19/Thong-tin-luc-luong-tran-Brighton-vs-Liverpool-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klavan s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, sao tr\u1ebb Nat Phillips \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, HLV Klopp s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Klavan ra \u0111i, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Italia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i, Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Klavan th\u00ec Divock Origi v\u00e0 Sheyi Ojo c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Anfield, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2328","checkdouble":"194419"},{"date":"00:33 14/08","title":"Sau Iniesta v\u00e0 Pique, th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chia tay \u0110T TBN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/sau-iniesta-va-pique-them-mot-tru-cot-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-dt-tbn.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Silva chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, sau Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Gerard Pique th\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo chia tay La Roja.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Silva tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110T TBN</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 David Silva chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay La Roja sau 12 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Man City, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Silva chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Silva chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/David-Silva-chia-tay-DT-Tay-Ban-Nha-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;David Silva chia tay \u0110T TBN</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDavid Silva ch\u01a1i cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2006, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay anh gi\u00e0nh 3 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, bao g\u1ed3m 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2008 v\u00e0 2012 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2010.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 125 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 35 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t. 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 World Cup 2014, Euro 2016 v\u00e0 World Cup 2018&nbsp;\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf B\u00f2 t\u00f3t \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018, T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i &quot;tiki-taka&quot; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u tho\u00e1i tr\u00e0o, David Silva mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Gerard Pique, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 3 chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David Silva vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 chia tay \u0110TQG</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 david Silva \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c th\u01b0 chia tay \u0111\u1ea7y x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Silva\" title=\"David Silva\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/162516-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Silva vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 chia tay \u0110T TBN</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0110T TBN, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110TQG \u0111\u00e3 cho t\u00f4i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi c\u00f3 12 n\u0103m v\u00e0 125 tr\u1eadn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T TBN&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ea3 World Cup v\u00e0 Euro c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng t\u01b0\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n NHM, L\u0110B\u0110 TBN, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c HLV, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u00fd \u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb9p trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;T\u00f4i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u00f4i trong bao n\u0103m qua, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u1ecd t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fac \u0110T TBN s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, t\u00f4i tin \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2327","checkdouble":"194420"},{"date":"06:05 14/08","title":"X\u1eed l\u00fd ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n, Petr Cech tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/xu-ly-ngo-ngan-petr-cech-tro-thanh-tro-cuoi-tren-mang-xa-hoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Petr Cech b\u1ecb Leverkusen tr\u00eau t\u1ee9c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha x\u1eed l\u00fd ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00ednh Cech sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t g\u1eaft.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Cech g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Arsenal b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Leverkusen. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19, HLV Unai Emery quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Petr Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u1ea3 quan. Arsenal th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates v\u00e0 Cech c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. HLV Emery ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng ngay ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi CH S\u00e9c l\u1ea1i lu\u00f4n g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 \u1edf nh\u1eefng pha chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Petr Cech b\u1ecb Leverkusen tr\u00eau t\u1ee9c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Petr Cech b\u1ecb Leverkusen tr\u00eau t\u1ee9c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/xu-ly-ngo-ngan-petr-cech-tro-thanh-tro-cuoi-tren-mang-xa-hoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Petr Cech b\u1ecb Leverkusen tr\u00eau t\u1ee9c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Matteo Guendouzi, Cech thay v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Hector Bellerin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eb3ng v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n, b\u00f3ng \u0111i s\u1ea1t c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc, su\u00fdt t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u00e0n c\u00e3i v\u00e3 v\u1edbi Leverkusen</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Twitter ti\u1ebfng Anh c\u1ee7a Leverkusen \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t video ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Bernd Leno, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u00fa th\u00edch b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi: \u201cNh\u00ecn v\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cech\" title=\"Cech\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/HLV-Unai-Emery-noi-ve-Arsenal-sau-tran-thua-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Arsenal \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Cech l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c d\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc. Petr Cech b\u1ecb Leverkusen tr\u00eau t\u1ee9c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 d\u00f9ng ch\u00ednh Twitter ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3: \u201c\u1ede Arsenal, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb quan tr\u1ecdng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d, anh vi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 thao l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n d\u1ea1y cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n khi c\u00e1c CLB kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng chia s\u1ebb c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00edch danh,\u00a0 Leverkusen \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i: \u201cCh\u00e0o Petr. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00f9a c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p Leno, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb r\u1ebd sang m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh\u201d, Leverkusen \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean Twitter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111\u00f9a gi\u1ee1n th\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chia s\u1ebb t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u00e0 ch\u00fac b\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng CLB l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t. Pha c\u1ee9u thua 1 vs 1 v\u1edbi Aguero l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t!\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-arsenal-02-man-city-sterling-va-cau-tra-loi-cho-ca-nuoc-anh-172-194405.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal 0-2 Man City: Sterling v\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-thuyet-phuc-cua-man-city-truoc-arsenal-172-194359.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-pep-team-khong-ngu-quen-tren-chien-thang-172-194353.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: \u201cPep Team\u201d kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-toi-muon-cac-cau-thu-arsenal-co-trach-nhiem-hon-172-194391.html\">HLV Emery: T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-noi-gi-ve-chien-thang-truoc-arsenal-172-194368.html\">Pep n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2326","checkdouble":"194421"},{"date":"06:28 14/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh Inter ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/tan-binh-inter-hoan-tat-giac-mo-thoi-tho-au.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Inter Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Keita Balde d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Monaco. Trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Nerazzurri.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Keita r\u1eddi Lazio \u0111\u1ebfn Monaco</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKeita Balde Diao l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng xa l\u1ea1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Inter Milan. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Lazio ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Serie A. Th\u00e1ng 8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, anh chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u01a1i cho Monaco t\u1ea1i Ligue 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y t\u1edbi t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Lazio v\u00e0 Keita. Sang Monaco, anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 23 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Ligue 1. Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, Keita nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb CLB trong m\u01a1, Inter Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Inter Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Keita Balde h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Inter Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Keita Balde h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Keita-gia-nhap-Inter.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Inter Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Keita Balde</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Gia nh\u1eadp Inter</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nInter Milan ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Keita Balde d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Monaco. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho Nerazzurri d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00eda 6 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Inter c\u0169ng c\u00e0i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Senegal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, Keita th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn Inter l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c. \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac\u201d, anh n\u00f3i tr\u00ean k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Inter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Italia v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. Khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho Inter v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Inter. H\u1ecd lu\u00f4n t\u1eed t\u1ebf v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1ef1. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang t\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m vui cho h\u1ecd m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n1h30 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 2 t\u1edbi (20/8), Inter s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. H\u1ecd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Sassuolo t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Serie A 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Serie A tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ac-milan-chi-110-trieu-euro-mua-milinkovicsavic-176-194386.html\">C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pogba Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hlv-massimiliano-allegri-phat-bieu-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-176-194396.html\">Ronaldo ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, HLV Juventus n\u1ed5 vang</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-o-he-2018-176-194317.html\">Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\">Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo-176-194058.html\">C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C \u0111\u1ed5i sang logo m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2325","checkdouble":"194422"},{"date":"06:54 14/08","title":"H\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u00e1ch Emery c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a Arsenal t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/3/hoc-tro-mach-emery-cach-dua-arsenal-tim-lai-chien-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alexandre Lacazette. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng HLV Unai Emery ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed c\u1ea3 hai trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Aubameyang l\u00e0m lu m\u1edd Lacazette</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlexandre Lacazette gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2017/18 t\u1eeb Lyon v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 47 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Sau m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9. T\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i cho t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m nay, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 4 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang t\u1eeb Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi cho Arsenal. 13 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eeda cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon ghi t\u1edbi 10 b\u00e0n cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alexandre Lacazette h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alexandre Lacazette h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Truoc-tran-Atletico-vs-Arsenal-Thap-sang-niem-hy-vong-tu-Lacazette-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alexandre Lacazette</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 hai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 song h\u00e0nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAubameyang \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Arsenal khi h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Man City t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t khi Lacazette \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i 29 tu\u1ed5i tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi nhau th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n theo h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1ea1c quan\u201d, Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alexandre Lacazette tr\u00ean ESPN. \u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa ch\u00fang t\u00f4i khi c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f9ng \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nhau v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City v\u1eeba qua.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i d\u1ea1t tr\u00e1i n\u1ebfu Lacazette \u1edf trung t\u00e2m. C\u1ea3 hai ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Aubameyang ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Unai Emery. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi\u201d, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Dortmund n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi Man City r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n sau tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea. Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t, gia t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 pressing v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-toi-muon-cac-cau-thu-arsenal-co-trach-nhiem-hon-172-194391.html\">HLV Emery: T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thierry-henry-sap-tro-lai-anh-doi-dau-arsenal-172-194380.html\">Thierry Henry s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-su-dung-cech-va-loai-bo-leno-172-194371.html\">HLV Emery n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Cech v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Leno?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-noi-gi-ve-chien-thang-truoc-arsenal-172-194368.html\">Pep n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-thuyet-phuc-cua-man-city-truoc-arsenal-172-194359.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2324","checkdouble":"194423"},{"date":"15:44 13/08","title":"Real l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cu\u1ed7m m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/154205-tien-ve-Tuchel.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m \u0111au l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Barcelona, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong th\u1eddi gian kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Rabiot</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho, Barcelona \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 Barca t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Barca v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Nasser Al Khelaifi c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. Ch\u1ea3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a PSG c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi h\u00e3ng h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Qatar Airways.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/154205-tien-ve-Tuchel.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi Qatar Airways song g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u00e9p gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u, g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha li\u1ec1n tr\u1edf m\u1eb7t ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi Rakuten c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00f4 t\u00ecnh, Barca \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft o\u00e1n v\u1edbi PSG. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Marco Verratti v\u00e0 Rabiot cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Real m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 Diario Gol c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2n hi\u1ec3m ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Barcelona. M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa PSG v\u00e0 Real l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Barca-muon-mua-Arturo-Vidal-voi-gia-30-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Real c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t \u0111i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Luka Modric. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n b\u1ecb lung l\u1ea1c. Theo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, Modric \u0111ang g\u00e2y t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric song Real c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u01a1i v\u00e0o tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c chia tay s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu, Los Blancos s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Rabiot t\u1edbi PSG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-sau-khi-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-172-194240.html\">HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Real?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ai-o-real-madrid-da-khuyen-kovacic-ra-di-cap-ben-chelsea-172-194208.html\">Ai \u1edf Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 khuy\u00ean Kovacic ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chot-eriksen-thay-modric-180-194307.html\">Real Madrid chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/them-mot-tien-dao-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-real-madrid-180-194385.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2323","checkdouble":"194389"},{"date":"14:57 13/08","title":"Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u mai 14/8.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ngang ng\u1eeda Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguyen Thanh Vinh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/2/8/muon-hagl-thua-nhieu-de-kiem-nghiem-ban-linh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh mu\u1ed1n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh v\u1eabn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i: <em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng D Pakistan s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018. </em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra sao, nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec BHL \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n t\u00ednh to\u00e1n r\u1ea5t k\u0129. Th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t sung v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung d\u00e0nh cho kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1\u201d.<br>\r\n</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Pakistan so v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam:<em> \u201cD\u1eabu sao, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Pakistan c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1. </em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>T\u00f4i ngh\u0129, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u0103m d\u00f2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc tri\u1ec3n khai th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ghi b\u00e0n\u201d.</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Vinh c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D Asiad 2018. Song \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0103n \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u th\u00ec h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00e0ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-quan-olympic-pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194384.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/thu-quan-olympic-pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-quan-olympic-pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194384.html\">Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan Saddam Hussain \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00ecnh s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i  m\u1eb7t, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2322","checkdouble":"194390"},{"date":"17:01 13/08","title":"HLV Emery: \"T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/hlv-emery-toi-muon-cac-cau-thu-arsenal-co-trach-nhiem-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo m\u1edf t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i Juve</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Juventus chi t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u01b0a Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Real Madrid. \u1ede tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Juve, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bianconeri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Real sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3, anh ghi t\u1edbi 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 438 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Los Blancos. Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 hung th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Juventus khi l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi h\u1ecd t\u1edbi 10 l\u1ea7n sau 7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay t\u1ea1i Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/hlv-massimiliano-allegri-phat-bieu-ve-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo m\u1edbi ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ch\u00ednh Ronaldo l\u00e0 t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00fap Real v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Juventus v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3 sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Allegri m\u1eebng r\u1ee1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 22 n\u0103m qua, Juventus ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro, HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Massimiliano Allegri noi ve tran Real Madrid vs Juventus\" title=\"Massimiliano Allegri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/hlv-juventus-neu-chung-toi-vao-ban-ket-cung-hoan-toan-xung-dang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hy v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1edbn h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Scudetto, Coppa Italia v\u00e0 Si\u00eau c\u00fap Italia\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sport Italia. \u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 5 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League sau 5 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i g\u1eafng s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Juventus tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi-176-194082.html\">Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Juve \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-khong-muon-ban-daniel-rugani-cho-chelsea-172-194073.html\">Chi ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng, t\u1ea1i sao Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Rugani?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\">Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tiet-lo-max-allegri-da-tu-choi-real-madrid-mua-he-nay-184-194164.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Max Allegri \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2321","checkdouble":"194391"},{"date":"16:29 13/08","title":"Real v\u00e0 Barca nh\u1eadn tin vui v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/real-va-barca-nhan-tin-vui-vu-rabiot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Adriano Rabiot</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Adriano Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c PSG nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/real-va-barca-nhan-tin-vui-vu-rabiot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rabiot\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-rabiot-cua-psg-180-194389.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Adriano Rabiot</span>, khi m\u00e0 Mateo Kovacic \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea c\u00f2n Luka Modric mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Inter Milan th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c Los Blancos mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Rabiot, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3, PSG v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rabiot t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Rabiot\" title=\"tien ve Rabiot\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/154205-tien-ve-Tuchel.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Rabiot t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Rabiot v\u1edbi PSG ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, PSG s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n anh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, PSG c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu Barca v\u00e0 Real Madrid th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Rabiot l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 23, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Rabiot gi\u1eefa Barca v\u00e0 Real s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2320","checkdouble":"194392"},{"date":"15:38 13/08","title":"B\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 lo s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/bi-chu-nha-lam-kho-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tu-lo-san-tap-truoc-ngay-ra-quan-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi di chuy\u1ec3n ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng 50 km t\u1edbi s\u00e2n t\u1eadp do n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u00e2n t\u1eadp ngay c\u1ea1nh s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh.</h2><h2>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 lo s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Sutasoma t\u1ea1i Jakarta, Indonesia. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf s\u00e2n ch\u00ednh n\u00ean n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed s\u00e2n t\u1eadp cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n g\u1ea7n 50 c\u00e2y s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 lo s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 lo s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tu-lo-san-tap-truoc-ngay-ra-quan-tai-ASIAD-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u00e2n t\u1eadp ph\u1ee5 ngay c\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, lo ng\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 di chuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i, ph\u1ea3i \u0111i 4-5h \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, BHL Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi nh\u00f3m h\u1ecdp quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp s\u00e2n do BTC s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp.\u00a0Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e2n t\u1eadp trong khu c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p Samsung, c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n Haper Cikarang kho\u1ea3ng 8km.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec: \"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 chi ph\u00ed. C\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 t\u00ecm, ch\u1ecdn s\u00e2n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ASIAD s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn h\u01a1n l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111i 4-5 ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 th\u00ec s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t\".<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 xem th\u00eam k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 12/8, do b\u1ecb b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed t\u1eadp mu\u1ed9n l\u00fac 20h00 n\u00ean HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ee7y bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y v\u00e0 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1eadp chay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00ea-t\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0103n t\u1ed1i, ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u nay c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 16h00 \u0111\u1ebfn 17h30 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n khu c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p Samsung, Cikarang. Ng\u00e0y mai (14/8), th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng D ASIAD v\u1edbi Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00. Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan-168-194390.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan-168-194390.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2319","checkdouble":"194393"}]}